--- Logguer functions
-- Log, emit a warning within a plugin.
--
-- @module irccd.logger

--- Log something.
-- This will append a message into stdout only if irccd
-- runs in verbose mode.
-- @param message the message write
function logger.log(message)
end

--- Emit a warning.
-- Write a message to stderr even if verbosity is disabled
-- @param message the message to write
function logger.warn(message)
end

